,{"kind":"italic_en","text":"purposes; whether it be a place, or a time, or any affair or state or event that is meditated or intended or determined or appointed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see 1, first sentence:)] the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"utmost point,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"scope,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"degree,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of knowledge [and of any attainment]: (Bd and Jel in liii. 31:) [the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"utmost degree of proficiency: a consummate degree"},{"kind":"text","text":"of goodness and of any other quality: the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"age of puberty, virility, ripeness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"maturity:"},{"kind":"text","text":"the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sum, amount,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"product, resulting from addition"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"multiplication: a sum of money:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and particularly"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a considerable sum thereof:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cash,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ready money, consisting of dirhems"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of deenárs:"},{"kind":"text","text":"in this sense, post-classical: pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mabaAligu","text_ar":"مَبَالِغُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaga fulaAnN mabolagahu","text_ar":"بَلَغَ فُلَانٌ مَبْلَغَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mabolagatahu","text_ar":"مَبْلَغَتَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaga fiY AlEilomi AlmabaAliga","text_ar":"بَلَغَ فِى العِلْمِ المَبَالِغَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaga fiY Aljawodapi mabolagFA","text_ar":"بَلَغَ فِى الجَوْدَةِ مَبْلَغًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mina Aljawodapi","text_ar":"مِنَ الجَوْدَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": for explanations of all which, see 1. And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balagota min~aA kul~a mabolagK","text_ar":"بَلَغْتَ مِنَّا كُلَّ مَبْلَغٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Albulagiyna","text_ar":"البُلَغِينَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n3248","headword_ar":"مُبَلِّغٌ","root":"blg","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"One whose office it is, with other persons each of whom is thus called, to chant certain words, as the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iqaAmap","text_ar":"اـِقَامَة"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"&c., in a mosque."},{"kind":"text","text":"(See my “ Modern Egyptians, “ ch. iii.)]"}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}